This README covers all aspects of the backend framework, Firebase, for the use of the application .wavlength. 

- SWE Keisun Luc has main authorization of the .wavlength Firebase, with access being provided to the rest of team

- Use cases for Firebase include:
1. Core - In use
2. Authentication - In use 
3. Data Management 
4. Privacy and Security

- Authentication is set up, but not connected to frontend framework Flutter yet. 

- Cloud hosting will require additional integration with current full framework. 

- Firebase integation with Jira successful.

- Firebase integration with Slack (optional)

